metadata.name: Into the wind
metadata.description:
Despite the fact that a woman is a very fragile creature by nature, most often, a wild beast sits inside every woman!
You don't know how and where it will manifest itself.
She will probably scream a lot.
Or she will break the dishes.
Or maybe her wild beast loves speed?
Such that the wind trembled her hair, and the speedometer needle went beyond 200 km/h

They say that risking your life is stupid. And I think that it is much more stupid to live the measured years without feeling the taste of speed and adrenaline.
